{"type": "article", "id": 26450, "title": "披萨包装做得这么缤纷，也许真的会让你食欲大开", "description": "有助于刺激消费者的想象力和味蕾，也更能体现品牌活力四射的形象。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-05T13:36:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 4237, "name": "品牌重塑"}, {"id": 7642, "name": "PizzaExpress"}, {"id": 23439, "name": "Bulletproof"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 130, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170818LRZNSwtbeQ7mHYkC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>PizzaExpress 1965 年成立于英国伦敦，是一家专注于意式披萨的连锁休闲餐厅。它在中国有个和英文名不太相符的名字“马上诺”，在上海、深圳、香港以及北京等城市有多家分店。</p>\n<p>2014 年 7 月，联想控股旗下私募股权机构弘毅投资宣布，斥资约 9 亿英镑全资收购 PizzaExpress。</p>\n<p>最近，PizzaExpress 邀请伦敦设计公司 Bulletproof 为其更新了“ Cook at Home ”零售系列的包装设计，希望能在其“ One Brand ”战略的推进下，强化 PizzaExpress 餐厅与其零售品牌的紧密联系。简单来说，此番包装设计更新，意在让消费者在逛超市遇到 PizzaExpress 的零售产品时，一瞬间就能联想到其餐厅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170813UeQ8RLkNaYOD9riF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>“ Cook at Home ”零售系列在英国各大超市有售，全数 36 款产品自去年 4 月起开启了重塑品牌包装的过程，当然这一系列目前只在英国国内发售。</p>\n<p>大胆肆意的手写字体设计强化了产品本身的“真实感”，也令消费者更易分辨其种类。</p>\n<p>经典款与 Romana 新款分别用黑色背景与彩色背景区别开来，经典系列的配色更是取决于食材的原料与风味。银箔质感的品牌标识和亚光饰面则是 <a href=\"http://www.designweek.co.uk/pizzaexpress-brings-at-home-range-in-line-with-restaurant-brand/\">Bulletproof 宣称的为了强调 PizzaExpress 品质感所做的调整。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170814pHvdwk4jxaYNehLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170814N2YvJjdyfpVTqI1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">经典系列</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170815Z86ApPYenEVFLrgM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170815zKfHZIUBnuqD7t8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Romana 系列</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p>除了披萨外，意大利面、面包以及调味汁的包装也都用色更为大胆，加以 PizzaExpress 经典的条纹元素露出，以便于在货架上轻松脱颖而出。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170816VIuBOGtqod16ciyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">调味汁</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170816qiSkbjQHwVuzyMTX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">意大利面</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170817op9CrVeBWwsikRfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">面包</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p>另外一个值得注意的细节是，新款包装缩小了外包装上可见的内部食物“窗口”，而是邀请知名美食摄影师 Andy Seymour 根据每款产品拍摄了不同的食材组合图片放大显示于外包装上，辨识度较之可见的食物本身更高。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021708189mCprFu3zDXH1yKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.designweek.co.uk/pizzaexpress-brings-at-home-range-in-line-with-restaurant-brand/\">用 PizzaExpress 的话说</a>，“我们的设计方案提供一套完整的包装组合，它在设计元素上虽说突破了不少，却延续了品牌的统一调性，有助于刺激消费者的想象力和味蕾，也更能体现品牌活力四射的形象。”</p>\n<p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.designweek.co.uk/pizzaexpress-brings-at-home-range-in-line-with-restaurant-brand/\">Designweek</a></p>\n\n"}